"23:00, but close for lunch between 12:00 and 14:00, enter Tuesdays 12:00 - "
"14:00 here. If you are also closed on Tuesday between 17:30 and 18:00, set "
"this as well and so on."
msgstr ""
"E.g: if you are generally open on Tuesdays - as set above - from 9:30 to "
"23:00, but close for lunch between 12:00 and 14:00, enter Tuesdays 12:00 - "
"14:00 here. If you are also closed on Tuesday between 17:30 and 18:00, set "
"this as well and so on."

#: ../classes/modules/mod.openingtimes.closed.php:120
msgid ""
"Furthermore, do not enter times here that span midnight. If you are however "
"closed from - let's say - 11:00 PM Mondays to 1:00 AM Tuesdays, enter "
"\"Mondays 23:00 to 23:59\" as well as \"Tuesdays 0:00 to 1:00\"."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, do not enter times here that span midnight. If you are however "
"closed from - let's say - 11:00 PM Mondays to 1:00 AM Tuesdays, enter "
"\"Mondays 23:00 to 23:59\" as well as \"Tuesdays 0:00 to 1:00\"."

#: ../classes/modules/mod.openingtimes.closed.php:121
msgid ""
